responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "10B097E14ECC550DD11319890090C60C", "This is our moment for the Zephyr Wind. The ostraca will exonerate us from our disenfranchised past. We need only to invoke our ancestral memory to understand that our kindred desires are to be venerated. They have always been a part of us (thumping his chest, where flecks of essence shine through his skin), but now we reunite with them through these clay carvings.")
